# CAVEAT: Constitutional AI is L4 (Anthropic technical report, not
# peer-reviewed). Methodology is TRAINING-time RLAIF with constitutional
# critique. cheapcode's `mizaj_consult` is INFERENCE-time rule lookup.
# Different mechanism + lower source tier. Does not lift
# `mizaj_consult_tool_lifts_design_quality` above its current @>=0.45.
